6. exd5 { Capturing the pawn, opening up the e-file. } 6... Nxd5 7. Re1
{ Taking control over the half-open e-file. The pawn on  e5  now has been attacked twice. }
7... Bd6
{ A blunder, played hundreds of times. This move protects the pawn on  e5  , but it leaves the Knight on  d5  undefended! }
8. Bxd5 { Capturing a free piece @@StartBracket@@+6.0@@EndBracket@@. } *

