O-O Nf6 { Attacking the pawn on  e4  . } 5. d4
{ Deutz Gambit, an interesting pawn sacrifice. } 5... Bxd4
{ The best move for Black.   5...exd4  will transpose into some exciting variations of the Scotch Game, Scotch Gambit, Max Lange Attack. }
