d3 { Giuoco Pianissimo Variation } 4... Nf6 5. Ng5
{ Threatening a Knight fork on  f7  , not the most accurate move. } 5... O-O
{ Defending  f7  with King and Rook. } 6. Nxf7
{ This blunder has been played thousands of times!   6.Bxf7+  is equally bad @@StartBracket@@-3.0@@EndBracket@@. }
