5... Nxd4
{ This blunder will illustrate the big problem with Black's kingside... } 6.
Qh5+ { The start of a forced sequence. } 6... Ke7 7. Qf7+ Kd6 8. Qd5+ Ke7 9.
Ng6+ Ke8 10. Qf7# *

