{ Anti-Fried Liver Defense, A passive and dubious move played over 500,000 times, especially on lower levels!   Black didn't want to play  3...Nf6  because he is afraid of  4.Ng5  , with an attack on  f7  . With  h6  , Black prevents  Ng5  after playing  Nf6  . }
4. d4 { Challenging Black's center. } 4... Nxd4
{ A very poor move, played over 2,000 times. } 5. Nxe5
