O-O Nf6 { Attacking  e4  while getting ready to castle. } 5. Re1
{ Defending  e4  . } 5... O-O
{ 5...Nxe4  is possible, but it could be better to wait just one more move, because of  6.Rxe4  d5  7.Bxd5  Qxd5  8.Nc3  , attacking the Queen while defending the Rook.  Nc3  isn't possible in the main variation! }
