{ Sometimes, White does a counter-sacrifice. But this is just a bad move...   7.Rxe4  fails to  7...d5  8.Bxd5  Qxd5  9.Re1  e4  10.Nd4  Ne5  , with similar problems for White as in the main variation @@StartBracket@@-3.5@@EndBracket@@. }
