9. Qd3 { Threatening checkmate on  h7  , the only winning move! } 9... g6
{ Preventing checkmate. } 10. Qh3
{ Attacking the Knight on  h6  . If the Knight moves, it will be checkmate on  h7  . }
10... Kg7 { Defending the Knight. } 11. Qxh6+ { A brilliant Queen sacrifice! }
11... Kxh6
