Kg7 13. Bh6+ { Another good and necessary move, giving a check first! } 13...
Kg8 { The King is forced to go back to  g8  . } 14. Nxd8+
{ Another discovered check. White is already up a piece, and the attack is still going @@StartBracket@@+8.0@@EndBracket@@. }
