{ Dubois Réti Defense, Developing the second Knight while attacking  e4  .  Another common move-order that results in this position is via the Italian Game, Two Knights Defense:   @@StartFEN@@rnbqkbnr/pppppppp/8/8/8/8/PPPPPPPP/RNBQKBNR w KQkq - 0 1@@EndFEN@@  1.e4  e5  2.Nf3  Nc6  3.Bc4  Nf6  4.d4  exd4  . }
