{ This move gives White an edge while keeping the position relatively simple.   5.Qd5  may be even slightly better, but this can get very complicated after  5...Qh4  @@StartBracket@@+3.0@@EndBracket@@. }
5... Kxf7
{ 5...Kf8  should be answered with  6.Bd5  @@StartBracket@@+6.0@@EndBracket@@. }
